WEBVTT

1
01:09:38.710 --> 01:09:40.040 
首相先生
Prime Minister.

2
01:09:41.120 --> 01:09:43.120 
温斯顿 温斯顿
Winston. Winston.

3
01:09:44.420 --> 01:09:45.690 
昨天你批准了
Yesterday, you gave permission...

4
01:09:45.710 --> 01:09:47.080 
批准什么
What permission?

5
01:09:47.170 --> 01:09:48.960 
让我去见巴斯蒂安尼尼
For me to meet Bastianini.

6
01:09:49.050 --> 01:09:50.730 
我批准的是理论上
I sanctioned the theoretical exploration...

7
01:09:50.800 --> 01:09:51.800 
理论上
Theoretical?

8
01:09:51.890 --> 01:09:54.140 
去试探一下意大利提出的条件 仅此而已
...of what price Italy would ask. Nothing more.

9
01:09:54.220 --> 01:09:56.240 
- 我没有批准任何 - 如果你不允许
- I did not sanction any... - If you will not permit

10
01:09:56.260 --> 01:09:58.180 
和谈的继续深入
further exploration of a peace agreement,

11
01:09:58.270 --> 01:09:59.730 
那么我就辞职
then you will have my resignation.

12
01:09:59.810 --> 01:10:01.440 
别开玩笑了 爱德华
Don't be absurd, Edward.

13
01:10:01.520 --> 01:10:04.860 
- 我需要你 - 我不可能
- I need you. You know I do. - I will not stand by

14
01:10:04.940 --> 01:10:08.200 
眼睁睁地看着一群年轻人
to watch another generation of young men die

